classifier

Class Classifiers

  • java.lang.Object
    • classifier.Classifiers
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Scorer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BayesClassifier

    public abstract class Classifiers
extends java.lang.Object
implements Scorer
    The Classifiers class has the purpose of serving has a blueprint for a classifier. It has the methods needed to evaluate a classifier's performance without defining any specific behaviour of the classifier itself. A Classifiers object can return a list of predictions elaborated by a classifier
